&ldquo;I, Lord Gaston Onomee, invite you to enter the Arena A La Carte. Fire up the ovens. Raid the pantry. Bake delights that would make a connoisseur weep. THEN crush your enemies, see them driven before you. Be the one to taste victory and be the last chef standing in the Baking Battle Royale&rdquo;

Fantasy Food Fight is a &ldquo;take-that&rdquo; style card game where you combine Wet Stuff, Dry Stuff and Tasty Bits to bake dishes. Once a dish is ready, you throw it at another chef, who then draws Splat points. But watch out. Collect 8 Splat points and you&rsquo;re out of the game.  The last chef standing, wins.

Use Cinnamonster cards to defend, steal, glimpse the future, and much more.
